EN: If you see through his appearance, he is a very kind person.

ZH: 他一眼就能说穿别人的真实意图。
EN: He can see through other people's true intentions at a glance.

ZH: 她说穿了我的计划，给了我一个好的建议。
EN: She exposed my plan and gave me a good suggestion.

